{"tid":755450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Facebook在中國成立子公司     註冊資料轉眼被撤回","createTime":"2018-07-25T08:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T03:43:59.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e58bb6c3cb1c0dfc80a0843f45e78264ca2394fa","tid":755450,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T08:31:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image5.thenewslens.com/2018/7/fepnd30xeej1w13lif0q077h8a5pql.jpg?auto=compress&amp;h=648&amp;q=80&amp;w=1080\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage5.thenewslens.com%2F2018%2F7%2Ffepnd30xeej1w13lif0q077h8a5pql.jpg%3Fauto%3Dcompress%26h%3D648%26q%3D80%26w%3D1080&h=f4d2d3ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">photo credit: REUTERS/Ted S. Warren/達志影像</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFacebook在中國成立附屬公司，但一星期後註冊資料已被撤回。<br />\n<br />\n根據中國媒體報道，Facebook在中國註冊公司名字為臉書科技（杭州）有限公司，於上星期三（7月18日）成立，註冊資本為3000萬美元，法定人代表為張京梅，公司由香港的Facebook Hong Kong Limited 100%控股。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image2.thenewslens.com/2018/7/e49k4s36qt3xeq6b1j32w130qielpe.jpg?auto=compress&amp;q=80&amp;w=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.thenewslens.com%2F2018%2F7%2Fe49k4s36qt3xeq6b1j32w130qielpe.jpg%3Fauto%3Dcompress%26q%3D80%26w%3D750&h=2c90af9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">photo credit: 新浪財經微博截圖。</span><br />\n<br />\n據路透社報道，臉書科技（杭州）在註冊文件列出的業務包括網絡科技發展及相關服務、投資顧問及市場推廣服務。<br />\n<br />\n另外在6月初，中國商標網電子公告系統公示有Facebook的註冊商標「臉譜」。以上種種意味著Facebook為期十年的入華努力有了階段性進展。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過，《紐約時報》指，臉書科技（杭州）的註冊在周三（25日）已被撤回，中國的公司註冊網站找不到臉書科技（杭州）的資料，暫時不清楚原因。在微博，有網友表示發表臉書入華的文章會被刪除。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image5.thenewslens.com/2018/7/8itndhprzne9x6qx3xflfk2wrcaw2e.jpg?auto=compress&amp;q=80&amp;w=750\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage5.thenewslens.com%2F2018%2F7%2F8itndhprzne9x6qx3xflfk2wrcaw2e.jpg%3Fauto%3Dcompress%26q%3D80%26w%3D750&h=0490f504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">微博截圖。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFacebook發言人Debbie Frost早前回應《紐約時報》查詢時說，公司有意在淅江成立創新中心，支援中國的開發者、創科人士和初創企業。她指出Facebook在其他地方如法國、巴西、印度和韓國都有成立類似的公司，目的都是幫助當地的開發者和企業家。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》Facebook Hong Kong的年報及在公司註冊處的紀錄，當中顯示Facebook Hong Kong近月動作頻頻，包括於5月獲Facebook Global Holdings II, LLC注資3億港元。另外Facebook首席會計主任Susan Taylor於今年獲委託為 Facebook Hong Kong董事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/100546\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F100546&d=Np%2BGv8deJujE%2BcUgGCD%2FXW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=a8ef8f24\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/100546</a>"},{"pid":"786eaa2d8f0ca203626a354b68e3a819fa41fd4f","tid":755450,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T10:13:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13fc581b34d81c62f57c0ea759fbbaed3916981d","tid":755450,"uid":9887,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T10:29:19.000Z","msg":"朱閪伯格奶共奶到成隻狗咁逐隻腳趾逐隻腳趾罅咁奶<br />\n但係都被主人一腳伸開叫佢死遠啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e729e1ebc24d1ce0de415c5e3852bd894f0348","tid":755450,"uid":55597,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T10:34:50.000Z","msg":"大家咪以為比中國撤回，等於 facebook 唔會再送資料比中國<br />\n大家快 d delete 晒 facebook 旗下既產品最穩陣"},{"pid":"b0bbfb684f36870ece35535c36f3382d46043c29","tid":755450,"uid":56731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T10:39:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vZILtbZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FvZILtbZ.jpg&h=833623ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b013d8eac0e9a7f87c80e72bf8cb3721c9b0c446","tid":755450,"uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T12:56:22.000Z","msg":"支國冇以前咁封閉咁"},{"pid":"03a1de28927d40bfbce0e40c4c58708271b1e1af","tid":755450,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T01:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb934beb3e592a8f5924d220cb3dcaff1f2173ab","tid":755450,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T01:09:22.000Z","msg":"Condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7171116f8e3e8441d913397a9102a6461b5dc2cb","tid":755450,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T01:10:44.000Z","msg":"朱西你算吧啦,越搞越樣衰"},{"pid":"228e5e581cfc7f5ee1520636531539135290d093","tid":755450,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T01:41:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/7da/fa7/7dafa7f6f52aa1929a3cbf244ababdf66ac5b378_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2F7da%2Ffa7%2F7dafa7f6f52aa1929a3cbf244ababdf66ac5b378_n.jpg&h=ca0b4848&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af3c5482dc203bd663a6bf07376f82ac6eadba6b","tid":755450,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T03:43:59.000Z","msg":"證明豬西為左投共做左唔少野，甚至生個女都想揾習帝幫手改名，但外人始終係外人，注定「養唔熟」，越想投共偏唔比埋堆<br />\n<br />\n睇返當年投共既國民黨文官武將係咩下場先啦朱西"}]}